{
  "texts": [
    "The 4 items again were measured on a five-point, Likert-type scale (\"strongly disagree\" to \"strongly agree\"), including statements such as \"I seek out new ways to do things\" (α = 0.81, M = 3.56, SD = 0.78).",
    "Several demographic traits were also measured and included in the analysis.",
    "In addition to age, gender, income, education, and race/ethnicity, participants were asked about their current employment status.",
    "Categories were full-time, part-time, unemployed looking for work, and unemployed not looking for work.",
    "Data analysis."
  ]
}